Ahrefs,is,a,web,explorer,that,can,be,used,to,verify,link,validity,The,service,updates,every,minutes,and,includes,tools,to,show,link,domains,anchors,and,top,pages,within,a,domain,The,Ahrefs,API,is,offered,as,a,free,service,and,a,paid,service,Using,REST,calls,users,can,make,calls,to,retrieve,backlinks,and,other,data,The,API,also,exposes,the,Ahrefs,interface,to,be,integrated,into,third,party,applications,An,account,is,required,with,service